{"tid":1734331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［國際文宣］冷氣軍師同我入嚟救理大","createTime":"2019-11-18T10:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T12:51:06.000Z","uid":302917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"63d2f4540651e8eb55b638f319bba8d9680d9b86","tid":1734331,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"你可能有好多原因出唔到，或者你而家直情唔喺香港，唔緊要。只要你有手機同twitter ac，就可以增加理大學生被救機會，冇藉口唔做喇啩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">文宣重點：香港警察拘捕/攻擊急救人員及受傷人士，理大學生正面臨人道危機(humanitarian crisis)。香港警察雖然冇大舉開槍，但佢地嘅圍城戰略係有目的地要間接逼到學生絕望求死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n理大學生嘅受傷情況：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1196226111065059329?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1196226111065059329%3Fs%3D21&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1cc06910\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1196226111065059329%3Fs%3D21&h=778a495e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1196226111065059329?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196289087302295555?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196289087302295555%3Fs%3D21&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=471325c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196289087302295555%3Fs%3D21&h=6f530c37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196289087302295555?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lihkg_forum/status/1196304059046608896?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flihkg_forum%2Fstatus%2F1196304059046608896%3Fs%3D21&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=bed55553\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.co